{"title":"liunx终端美化（ubuntu）","date":"2020-07-10T03:45:31.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年7月10日","L":"2020/07/10","MM-DD":"07-10"},"author":"zao","link":"2020/07/10/articles/liunx终端美化（ubuntu）","tags":["liunx","terminal"],"categories":["articles"],"updated":"2020-07-10T03:45:31.000Z","content":"<h2 id=\"安装zsh\">安装zsh<a href=\"#安装zsh\" title=\"安装zsh\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"安装oh-my-zsh\">安装Oh-My-Zsh<a href=\"#安装oh-my-zsh\" title=\"安装Oh-My-Zsh\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh -c \"$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)\"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>有可能出现443，被墙了，则进行下列操作</p>\n<ol><li>在<a href=\"https://www.ipaddress.com/查询raw.githubusercontent.com的真实IP\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipaddress.com/查询raw.githubusercontent.com的真实IP</a></li>\n</ol><p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/ruoyiwen/img/raw/master/blog/20200709151916.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<ol><li>修改hosts文件</li>\n</ol><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>添加</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">199.232.68.133  raw.githubusercontent.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"安装zsh插件\">安装zsh插件<a href=\"#安装zsh插件\" title=\"安装zsh插件\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd ~/.oh-my-zsh/plugins</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ul><li><p><code>zsh-syntax-highlighting</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git $&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>zsh-autosuggestions</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions $&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>添加</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/ruoyiwen/img/raw/master/blog/20200709163436.png\" class=\"φcy\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"docker安装和使用","link":"2020/07/10/articles/docker安装和使用"},"next":{"title":"windows terminal加powershell7美化命令行操作","link":"2020/05/28/articles/windows-terminal加powershell7美化命令行操作"},"plink":"https://www.hansomezao.com/2020/07/10/articles/liunx终端美化（ubuntu）/","toc":[{"id":"安装zsh","title":"安装zsh","index":"1"},{"id":"安装oh-my-zsh","title":"安装Oh-My-Zsh","index":"2"},{"id":"安装zsh插件","title":"安装zsh插件","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"custom":"转载请加上署名!"}}